#This is for AWS
#Configure all entries needed for main.tf file
	* Provider
	* Resources
#Go to the terraform folder and execute 
	* terraform init # It should successful
#Export the access keys 
	* export AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=**************	
	* export AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=***************
	* terraform apply
        

######################

#Key usage for terraorm:-

* Set up Access keys for AWS account to be used by terraform 
$ cd ~
$ mkdir .aws
$ cd .aws
~/.aws$ vim credentials


[default]
aws_access_key_id = ACCESS_KEY
aws_secret_access_key = SECRET_KEY

~/.aws$ chmod 600 credentials 
* Set-up a key pair values

Create a key pairs in AWS
Download the key-pair
Move  the key-pair to .aws account 
~/Downloads$ cd ~/Downloads && mv mac-ssh.pem ../.aws/
Change the permission - chmod 400 mac-ssh.pem

